<h1 show_note>Show a note</h1>

<p>Gets note information.</p>

<pre>[GET] <hl>/api/v1/notes/:id</hl></pre>

<h2 show_note_example>Example</h2>

<pre>
curl -X GET \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -H 'Accept: application/json' \
  --oauth2-bearer AUTH_TOKEN \
  http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notes/:id
</pre>

